text: == Btissam Sadini Team Morocco Karate -61 KG == Bronze medal World Championship Madrid 2018 individual Silver medal African Championship Tangier 2020 individual Silver medal African Championship Tangier 2020 team Bronze medal African Games Rabat 2019 individual Gold medal African Games rabat 2019 team Gold medal African Championship Zone 1 Marrakech 2019 individual Bronze medal African Championship Gaborone 2019 individual Silver medal African Championship Kigali 2018 individual Bronze medal African Championship Kigali 2018 team Bronze medal Karate 1 Premier League Rabat 2017 Btissam Sadini is a Moroccan karateka. In 2018, she won one of the bronze medals in the women's kumite 61 kg event at the 2018 World Karate Championships held in Madrid, Spain. In 2018, she won silver medal in the African Championship in Rwanda. In 2019, she represented Morocco at the 2019 African Games and she won one of the bronze medals in the women's kumite 61 kg event. and gold medal kumite women´s team In 2019, she won the bronze medal in the African Championship in Botswana.
